          <div class="panel-body">
            <p>We are looking for a Scenic Artist for our Bermondsey scenery workshop with the following:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Excellent attention to detail and able to work in a team with other departments, liaising on materials, schedules and construction techniques etc.</li>
              <li>Minimum of 3 years’ experience of working in a similar environment.</li>
              <li>Based in busy paintshop, with other scenic artists to produce high quality painted scenery for theatre productions, fashion shows and events.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
