          <h3 class="panel-title" data-target="#panel-2" data-toggle="collapse">Metal Worker / Fabricator</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="panel-2">
          <div class="panel-body">
            <p>We are looking for an experienced Metalworker required for our Bermondsey scenery workshop, specialising in M.I.G welding in Mild Steel and Aluminium with the following:</li>
            <ul>
              <li>Excellent fabrication skills required and experience in machining / mechanical knowledge would be an advantage.</li>
              <li>Minimum of 3 years’ experience and must be able to work from CAD drawings.</li>
              <li>Will work closely with the Head of Fabrication and small team as well as other departments to liaise on materials, schedules and construction techniques.</li>
              <li>Assist in the maintenance and safe use of tools and equipment, adhering to health and safety guidelines.</li>
              <li>Based in busy workshop, fabricating and constructing for worldwide theatre productions, fashion shows and events</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="panel">
