          <h3 class="panel-title" data-target="#panel-3" data-toggle="collapse">CAD / Drawing Technician</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="panel-3">
          <div class="panel-body">
            <p>We are looking for an experienced Scenic Draughtsperson to prepare and update scenic construction drawings in order to assist in the production of scenery for our Bermondsey studio with the following:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Experience in the use of AutoCAD 2D and 3D for structural drawings within a built environment.</li>
              <li>Ability to produce detailed specification and construction drawings of scenic elements, using AutoCAD, Photoshop and/or manual drawing skills as appropriate.</li>
              <li>Minimum of 3 years’ experience experience in construction draughting. A detailed understanding of theatre structural engineering, metalwork, carpentry and scenic construction is a bonus.</li>
              <li>You will be required to produce technical specifications for scenic elements, research special materials / construction methods and order items as required.</li>
              <li>Able to work as part of a team and the ability to work to own initiative.</li>
            </ul>
